  <h1 class="h1">Hello from Lance!</h1>
  <p>My name is Lance and I'm a software engineer from the United States.</p>

  <section class="about" aria-label="About me">
    <Image
      src={myHeadshot}
      alt="My headshot"
      format="avif"
      width="600"
    />

    <div class="content">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquam architecto blanditiis culpa eaque facere fugiat hic, iure modi sed. Beatae blanditiis commodi cumque cupiditate debitis, deserunt dolor ea enim error et in iusto laudantium maxime nemo nostrum quo, sed voluptatem?</p>
      <Link
        style={"secondary"}
        text={"ðŸ‘‹ Say hi!"}
        href={"mailto:lancemonotone@gmail.com"}
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="recent-posts" aria-label="My recent posts">
    <h2 class="h2">Recent Posts</h2>
